 990:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rcc_ex.c **** * @brief Wait for CRS Synchronization status.
 991:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rcc_ex.c **** * @param Timeout  Duration of the timeout
 992:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rcc_ex.c **** * @note  Timeout is based on the maximum time to receive a SYNC event based on synchronization
 993:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rcc_ex.c **** *        frequency.
 994:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rcc_ex.c **** * @note    If Timeout set to HAL_MAX_DELAY, HAL_TIMEOUT will be never returned.
